<p>
<wintitle>Dialog Nibelung StudDB</wintitle> main menu consists of:
<ul>
<li><uicontrol>File</uicontrol> menu;</li>
<li><uicontrol>Subdivision</uicontrol> menu;</li>
<li><uicontrol>Student</uicontrol> menu;</li>
<li><uicontrol>Help</uicontrol> menu.</li>
</ul>
</p>

