<p>
Each command of the main menu can be invoked either by keyboard shortcut or selecting the item with a mouse. You can also access the main menu from the keyboard by pressing the <uicontrol><shortcut>Alt</shortcut></uicontrol> key.
</p>

<note type="tip">If the menu item is greyed out or does not respond to the shortcut, this means that the command is not available in current context. For example, you can not edit a student profile if no student is selected.</note>

